## PowerPoint (python-pptx) Guidelines

When generating PowerPoint instead of Word:
- Use the same color palette (Navy headers, Dark body)
- One key message per slide
- Data tables: max 6 rows visible (use appendix for detail)
- Include speaker notes in Woody's voice (reference `woodys-brain.mdc`)
- Chart preference: simple bar/line charts, no 3D effects

## Markdown Presentations (Marp/reveal.js)

For quick slide decks in Markdown:
```markdown
---
marp: true
theme: default
paginate: true
---

# Slide Title
## Subtitle

---

# Next Slide
- Bullet point with data
- Another point

<!-- Speaker notes go here -->
```
